source.name: Number of Structurally Deficient Bridges Map
source.description: Map showing the location of structurally deficient bridges counted among the more than 6,800 bridges that exist on the highway system (including the interstate highway system, the U.S. numbered highway system and the state numbered highway system) in the State of Oklahoma.
